		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Finally done the quest, well heres a bit of information to those whom wish these excellent articles.<BR>
<BR>
All the inforamtion is correct about the spawns.<BR>
<BR>
But heres how u get Hasten to spawn so you only have to wait 2 hours max.<BR>
<BR>
Firstly u must kill as many Lizards, Skels, Clops and Baslliks in the HG valley including the Dancing rock near the entrance from the scarabs. This does not include the HG. I got this from hints off a GM after i camped for 8 hours at his spawn spot in the Sphinx valley. Once i did all the above he was finally seen near the tower in HG Valley in about one hours time.<BR>
Do not attempt to kill the Monk whom is a alternate spawn. He killed a level 50 wiz and druid. He has speed faster than SOW.. and hits for 320.<BR>
<BR>
Also the good thing about trying to get Hasten to spawn also helps HG groups as the Clops, Skels and Basiliks are place holders for HG.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Thantalus Dagrimal<BR>
40th level Rogue
